text.tspan: Population growth rate with and without migration, United States
The annual change in population with migration included, versus the change if there was zero migration (neither emigration or immigration).
The latter therefore represents the change in population based solely on domestic births and deaths.
Data source: United Nations, World Population Prospects (2022)
